en." Pediat Pulm 31 (2001): 314-6[4] Kovesi TA, Swartz R, MacDonald N "Transient renal failure due to simultaneous ibuprofen and aminoglycoside therapy in children with cystic fibrosis." N Engl J Med 338 (1998): 65-6[5] Assael BM, Chiabrando C, Gagliardi L, Noseda A, Bamonte F, Salmona M "Prostaglandins and aminoglycoside nephrotoxicity." Toxicol Appl Pharmacol 78 (1985): 386-94[6] Zarfin Y, Koren G, Maresky D, et al "Clinical and laboratory observations: possible indomethacin-aminoglycoside interaction in preterm infants." J Pediatr 106 (1985): 511-3', 1767363023);
